#META# contentSummary: An order sent from *al-Dīwān al-Ikhtiyārī *to the *muʿtamid* ʿAlī b. ʿAbd al-Rashīd to withhold the payment of 2 dīnārs and one *dāng*, which a certain Abū Bakr Yaʿqūb b. Abū Naṣr requested. It appears that a *dīwān* representative is being sent to the area in order to deal with the situation.
